  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cafferen\" title=\"House Cafferen\"><img alt=\"House Cafferen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/50px-House_Cafferen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/75px-House_Cafferen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/100px-House_Cafferen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Jon Cafferen</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Cafferen\" title=\"House Cafferen\"><img alt=\"House Cafferen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/50px-House_Cafferen.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/75px-House_Cafferen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/28/House_Cafferen.svg/100px-House_Cafferen.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Cafferen\" title=\"House Cafferen\">House Cafferen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlander\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Stormlander\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Oakheart\" title=\"Alys Oakheart\">Alys Oakheart</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table> \n<p><b>Jon Cafferen</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cafferen\" title=\"House Cafferen\">House Cafferen</a> and the heir to <a href=\"/index.php/Fawnton\" title=\"Fawnton\">Fawnton</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon I Targaryen\">Aegon I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Cafferen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser Jon married <a href=\"/index.php/Alys_Oakheart\" title=\"Alys Oakheart\">Alys Oakheart</a>, the daughter of the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Oak\" title=\"Old Oak\">Old Oak</a>, in <a href=\"/index.php/12_AC\" title=\"12 AC\">12&#160;AC</a>. During the <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wedding\">wedding</a>, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Wyl_of_Wyl\" title=\"Wyl of Wyl\">Wyl of Wyl</a> turned up uninvited and was admitted through the postern gate by a treacherous servant. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Oakheart\" title=\"House Oakheart\">Oakheart</a> and most of the guests were slain, and Jon's wife was forced to watch him be <a href=\"/index.php/Eunuch\" title=\"Eunuch\">castrated</a>. His wife and her <a href=\"/index.php/Handmaid\" title=\"Handmaid\">handmaids</a> were gang-raped by Wyl's men and then sold off to a <a href=\"/index.php/Myr\" title=\"Myr\">Myrish</a> slaver. This was the most infamous act of the <a href=\"/index.php/First_Dornish_War\" title=\"First Dornish War\">First Dornish War</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jon_Cafferen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabreign_of_the_dragon_-_the_wars_of_king_aegon_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Reign of the Dragon - The Wars of King Aegon I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122905\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.086 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.293 seconds\nPreprocessor vi